1. Molim vas, koliko *goriva* ima u vašem automobilu? (Please, how much *fuel* is in your car?)
2. Oni su potrošili puno *goriva* tokom putovanja. (They used a lot of *fuel* during the trip.)
3. *Gorivo* za ovaj motor mora da bude visokog kvaliteta. (The *fuel* for this engine must be of high quality.)
4. U našoj zemlji postoji velika zavisnost od uvoza *goriva*. (Our country is heavily dependent on imported *fuel*.)
5. Ova pumpa prodaje različita vrsta *goriva*, uključujući benzin, dizel i plin. (This gas station sells different types of *fuel*, including gasoline, diesel, and gas.)
6. On je izlio *gorivo* po celom podu. (He spilled *fuel* all over the floor.)
7. *Gorivo* je potrebno za pokretanje ovog motora. (Fuel is required to operate this engine.)
8. Vozač je otišao da sipa *gorivo* u svoj automobil. (The driver went to refuel his car with *fuel*.)
9. Ovaj kamion koristi više *goriva* od drugih vozila. (This truck consumes more *fuel* than other vehicles.)
10. Da li znate gde se nalazi najjeftinija cena *goriva* u gradu? (Do you know where the cheapest *fuel* price is in town?)